Visualize Calculated Insights for a Vehicle

Add the Vehicle Calculated Insights Vehicle Page Parent Card flexcard to the Vehicle record page so that sales and service teams can view calculated insights directly in the app. The flexcard shows the latest values as synced from Data Cloud for vehicle lifetime value, the total count of cases, and the count of open cases.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Data Cloud and Automotive are enabled.

Who: Users must have the Data Cloud Metrics Visualization permission set assigned to them.
